title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Beechcraft 17 - version 1.0
description:
In this video we are going to have a look at the first Famous Flyer released by Asobo for MSFS 2020: the Beechcraft 17. After a short review of the various liveries we will take the aircraft out for a flight but not before we inspected both the interior and exterior of it. Once that is completed we go airborn and perform a short flight.
